  Fridrich-1998               64.3 MB/s
  YeHuang-2018                10.2 MB/s
  YeHuang-2018-Optimized      10.8 MB/s
  LSCM-2020                   11.1 MB/s




SIMD + tiling experiment

cd .. && rm -rf build && mkdir build && cd build
cmake .. -DYEH_USE_FAST_SIN=ON -DCHAOS_DIFFUSE_KERNEL=1 -DCHAOS_DIFFUSE_TILE_BYTES=16384
cmake --build . --target show_flags
make -j"$(nproc)"
./imgcrypt_bench


